data.description: Welcome to a delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the Autumn Woods subdivision. This residence offers an open floor plan that seamlessly connects its main spaces. The living room is spacious with cathedral ceilings, featuring a gas fireplace for cozy gatherings. The kitchen is well-equipped with tile countertops, an electric cooktop stove, and a full pantry. A two-car garage provides convenience. The primary bedroom offers ample space with an en suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The interior of this home features brand new paint throughout. The sunroom is a versatile area with removable sun shades and a built-in bar. The backyard boasts a large deck and an above-ground pool, complemented by a shed for extra storage. Conveniently located near Hwy 42 in the heart of Prairieville, this home combines comfort with a great location. Seller willing to contribute $3000 towards buyers closing costs.
